reviewText: UGH, why only two episodes?! This show is hilarious!! Super raunchy and awkward, but the art is pretty good and the characters are pretty well thought out. I'm sad there's not more.
Good just English subtitles. It would have been nice to have English voice actors and actresses.

It's unfortunate this series is only two episode, but it's two extremely sexy episodes. The art is great, the character design is great, the voice acting is pretty nice, and overall this anime is enjoyable.....if you're perverted. It's not your run-of-the-mill ecchi, since it depicts more than just panties. The only bad thing is, as I said, it's two episodes. It's still worth the money.

Bought this in store from FYE a few weeks ago. Well...there isn't really a story, but rather an OVA that's in two parts. The story is basically what the box says, but its a lot more sexual than what it describes. If you are looking for an ecchi (bodering hentai)  about underage girls (16 yrs old I think), then this is for you. If not, don't waster your money.
